# Mario Game using Pygame

A simple Mario game created using the Pygame library. In this game, you control Mario to avoid obstacles and earn points. The game features a dragon, flames, and dynamic level changes.

## Screenshots

![Gameplay Screenshot](screenshots/gameplay.png)

## Features

- Control Mario using arrow keys.
- Dodge obstacles and collect points.
- Dynamic level changes based on score.

## Resources

- Images: Place image files in the project directory.
- Sounds: Place sound files in the project directory.

